title: Misfits - Misfits (Anthology)
description:
Misfits - Misfits (contains previously unreleased versions) (mp3 320 Kbps)

Everything that made the Misfits is here, including the odd remix, alternate take, and re-edited version. The band is loud and defiant, as is Glenn Danzig, whose considerable vocal chops are well displayed here. The perfect music for an evening of headbanging or watching gore films. Collectors who don&#039;t want to invest in the box set should note that this is also the only place to get "London Dungeon" and "Ghouls&#039; Night Out," the B-sides of the "Night of the Living Dead" single.
